* planning_order_id or planning_group_id
* grade
* qty_mt
* heat_number_seq
* upstream_route
* casting_group if relevant
* compatibility_class

### ScheduledOperation

Machine-level scheduled task.

Fields:

* operation_id
* parent_object_type
* parent_object_id
* resource_id
* operation_type
* start_time
* end_time
* setup_before
* lateness_cost
* sequence_position

### ReleaseObject

Execution handoff object.

Fields depend on how MES wants to receive execution instructions.

